{"tid":2358251,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是普午 親子丼 配 日式餃子 七味墨魚咀","createTime":"2021-01-08T04:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T09:19:52.000Z","uid":33359,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6c2883df42487c99cbf91ce60b48d6a7144e6a","tid":2358251,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGaWbAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGaWbAX.jpg&h=4ea24561&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Uy1nHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Uy1nHF.jpg&h=6253e477&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OURBV2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOURBV2H.jpg&h=46e7d003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n親子丼既強有啲過熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能係拎返公司太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n焗到熟哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉幾滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個調味我唔太鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日式餃子普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墨魚咀已經唔夠香了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為個盒既倒汗水有啲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墨魚咀濕哂淋哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落口麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb61eaaa68de5c9bbb56ec7dc716c056223ac20","tid":2358251,"uid":14208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"尋日去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a675befb4181a646b97f170e7d